[I]      First off, is there a timer between times you can sleep?  Me, being a mage, can use up a lot of mana fast and when I teleport back to the bed I am using, it says something like This is no time to sleep.  Then I have to sit around a while and wait for it to let me to rest so I can get my mana back and then waist it in about 5 minutes trying to kill tough guys.  To me this is very frustrating, having to rest every 5 minutes and then waiting for me to be able to rest, unless there is no timer and I am doing something wrong.  Does it get any better off for a mage?  How do you other mages handle it?[/I][/QUOTE]

